00:04:08.140 --> 00:04:09.939
food businesses.

00:04:09.939 --> 00:04:16.810
My job is to come up with these food business
ideas and then to work with my colleagues,

00:04:16.810 --> 00:04:21.150
who are food technologists and chefs, and
in the case of about 10 of them, they are

00:04:21.150 --> 00:04:25.440
