00:12:33.829 --> 00:12:36.730
Some people have this incredible density of
taste buds.

00:12:36.730 --> 00:12:40.430
Their entire tongue is densely packed with
these taste buds.

00:12:40.430 --> 00:12:44.899
Then some people at the other end of the spectrum
have just a few dotted around.

00:12:44.899 --> 00:12:51.620
This person, whose tongue is covered with
taste buds, will experience the tastes as

00:12:51.620 --> 00:12:58.130
three times as intense as the person who has
less taste buds.

00:12:58.130 --> 00:13:00.310
Imagine that you've got all these taste buds.

00:13:00.310 --> 00:13:06.050
Something that's bitter to you is going to
be much more bitter than it is to someone.

00:13:06.050 --> 00:13:10.440
Salty is saltier, sweet is sweeter, spicy
is spicier.

00:13:10.440 --> 00:13:13.480
We know this by counting the taste buds on
your tongue.

