00:44:39.440 --> 00:44:42.520
It's working on the same fibers as pain.

00:44:42.520 --> 00:44:44.140
Take a fork and jab it into your tongue.

00:44:44.140 --> 00:44:49.460
[laughter] [laughs] That's basically what
